o be different individuals, we perceive many beings/objects within undivida=
ble Aatman, find some attractive and some repulsive, develop desires and no=
tions like happiness and sadness, etc. All this is under the tremendous pow=
er of Shakti or divine Mother. When the big force within ocean (which is no=
