When Mother Kalaratri takes control over the cosmos, it is like the oce=
anic force calming down and all waves and ripples becoming still. All being=
s (slaves of Shakti) cease activities and lose their fears and other agenda=
s. They are all in bliss. She takes control of all the worlds. Of course, t=
his applies to Mother Kalaratri taking control over the inner cosmos as wel=
l!
